title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Heath/Hayes/Micheletti
description: Nordo is back in the big chair to fill in for PA! MNUFC Head Coach Adrian Heath joins the show to talk Loons, Dan Hayes from The Athletic talks Twins, and plenty of puck talk with Pat Micheletti!
